TaskName:Master

TaskSpr:!master

SupportURL:http://www.stevefryatt.org.uk/software/games/

URLFailed:Could not find an application to launch the given URL.

NotComplete:The line is not complete for scoring.

Guess:Guess the code
Correct:Correct! Well done!
Slow:Too slow! Bad luck

# Interactive Help Messages

Help.IconBar:\TMaster application.|MIt plays a sequence guessing game.|M\Sstart a new game.

Help.Main:\Tmain Master \w.|MIt plays a sequence guessing game.
Help.Main.Pool:\Dpick a coloured counter to drop on the grid.
Help.Main.Guess:\Tguessing grid.|MDrag coloured pegs from the grid above and drop them in the current row to make a guess.|M\Dre-order or remove pegs already placed in the current row.
Help.Main.Mark:\Tscoring grid.|MWhite pegs indicate a correct colour in the wrong place.|MBlack pegs indicate a correct colour in the correct place.
Help.Main.Display:\Tinformation field.|MWatch the text for details of the game's progress.
Help.Main.Score:\Tscore for the last round.
Help.Main.HiScore:\Tbest score achived so far in the game.
Help.Main.New:\Sclear the board and start a new game.
Help.Main.Process:\Sask the computer to mark the current guess.

Help.Info:\Tprogram information \w for the Master application.
Help.Info.Website:\Tprogram information \w for the Master application.|M\Svisit its website for information and updates.

Help.MainMenu.00:\Sstart a new game.

Help.IconBarMenu.00:\Rto see information about Master and visit its website.
Help.IconBarMenu.01:\Sread the Master documentation.
Help.IconBarMenu.02:\Stoggle whether or not drags in the Master window use a representation of a peg or a dashed box.
Help.IconBarMenu.03:\Squit Master.

